  [Text] Madrid 24 Mar (JANA) -- The brother Secretary of the 
General People's Committee for External Liaison and 
International Cooperation ['Umar Mustafa al-Muntasir] met with 
Spanish Foreign Minister Javier [Madariaga] Solana, in Madrid 
yesterday. 
  Bilateral relations, ways to develop and promote them, and 
