<F P=106> [Unattributed report: "Interparliamentary Union Conference </F>
in Paris Supports UN Resolution on Hebron Massacre"] 
  [Text] On Monday, 21 March, [French] National Assembly 
Speaker Philippe Seguin expressed the "support" of the 
Interparliamentary Union Conference for the UN resolution 
condemning the massacre of Palestinians at the Hebron mosque. 
Mr. Seguin emphasized that the conference is "very sensitive to 
