<F P=102>  AU2703154094 Frankfurt/Main FRANKFURTER ALLGEMEINE in German 
26 Mar 94 p 4 </F>

<F P=103> AU2703154094 </F>
<F P=104>  Frankfurt/Main FRANKFURTER ALLGEMEINE </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> German </F>
Article Type:BFN 

<F P=106> ["epd" report: "Bonn Development Aid for Tunisia"] </F>
  [Text] Bonn, 25 Mar -- The Federal Government has promised 
56.3 million marks [DM] in development aid to Tunisia. Of that, 
DM31.3 million need not be repaid. The country gets support 
for, among other things, steps to save water, the FRG Ministry 
of Economic Cooperation and Development announced in Bonn on 
Friday [25 March]. Tunisia will soon have developed all water 
reservoirs, while consumption will continue to increase. 

